Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 9 January 2023

Welcome to AiAo! We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect information in relation to our mobile app, AiAo, and your choices about the collection and use of your information.

1. Information We Collect

a. Mandala Drawings: Our App allows you to create mandala drawings, which we collect and analyze using a machine learning model to enhance your experience.

b. Kalimba Melodies: You can record melodies using the kalimba feature in our App. These recordings are stored locally on your device and are not shared with any third parties.

c. Self-Test Data: Our App includes a self-test feature using the Zung Self-Rating Anxiety Scale. We collect your responses to generate an anxiety rating and to create an overall trend analysis over a week. All data older than 7 days is automatically deleted.

2. Use of Information

The information we collect is used to:

Provide, maintain, and improve our App.
Analyze how you use the App for improving the user experience.
Understand and analyze trends in user activity.
3. Sharing of Information

We do not share your personal information with third parties, except as required by law.

4. Data Storage and Security

We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

5. Childrenâ€™s Privacy

Our App does not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13.

6. Data Retention and Deletion

We retain the collected data for as long as necessary to provide the services of our App. If you delete AiAo, all data will be erased from our servers.

7. Changes to Our Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at dgs.arthealing@gmail.com .
